Around a hundred fans were still gathered around the offices after the incident. (Source: Twitter) Around a hundred fans were still gathered around the offices after the incident. (Source: Twitter)

A group of Porto fans exploded fireworks outside the headquarters of Juventus in Turin ahead of the teamsâ€™ Champions League match on Tuesday.

